Class StoreDefault

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xceptance.xlt.nocoding.scriptItem.storeDefault.StoreDefault

    public abstract class StoreDefault
extends java.lang.Object
implements ScriptItem
    The abstract class for every default store item. A default store item is an item that sets the default value for certain fields. These fields are specified by Constants.PERMITTEDLISTITEMS.
